<body><div class="viewoption"><p><span class="shippinganddelivery">Shipping and Delivery Policy &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span class="viewshipping">French Connection.in strives to deliver the Products purchased&nbsp; in excellent condition and in fastest time i:e within 7 working days (not including Sundays and public holidays) from the date of order confirmation, and will be delivered to the customers address within 5 working days after order is shipped. However in some cases the order can take up to 10 &ndash; 12 working days for delivery depending on the location of delivery.</span></p><ul><li>The customer can purchase online for any value i:e&nbsp; there is no minimum purchase order value.</li><li><strong>We offer free shipping for all products</strong>.</li><li>You will receive an order confirmation by Email and SMS on completing your order.</li><li>As long as the package has not left our warehouse, the order may be cancelled. Cancellations can be carried out by contacting our&nbsp;Customer Service on&nbsp;<strong>1800-22-8288 (Mon-Fri, 9 AM - 7 PM)</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>. If the package has already left our warehouse, we won&rsquo;t be able to cancel the order.</li><li>Orders cannot be placed through Email / Post / Fax.</li><li>You may track shipping status of your orders on our website www.frenchconnection.in or by calling our customer care number.</li><li>The courier will attempt delivery twice if the door is locked and alternatively you can contact the local courier office with the docket number and update them on the timings for delivery. Currently, each order may be shipped only to a single destination address. If you would like to ship products to different addresses, you will need to place multiple orders.</li><li>To ensure that your order reaches you in the fastest time and in good condition, we only ship through reputed courier agencies.</li><li>If you believe that the product is not in good condition or if the packaging is tampered with or damaged, before accepting delivery of the goods, please refuse to take delivery of the package, and call us on 1-800-22-8288&nbsp; or mail us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:customercare@frenchconnection.in">customercare@frenchconnection.in</a>&nbsp;, mentioning your order reference number. We shall make our best efforts to ensure that a replacement delivery is made to you at the earliest.</li><li>Our valuable customers need to submit all necessary VAT / statutory forms which are mandatory according to the state government rules for any shipments coming in from other states as and when applicable. Our customer service personnel will get in touch with you regarding this if there is a requirement from the Courier Company.</li><li>You will be able make your purchases on our site from anywhere in the world with credit/debit cards issued in India, but please ensure the delivery address is in India.</li></ul></div></body>